Q : Could you please explain use of Flexbox in react-native ?
A : The Flexbox is design to provide a consistance layout on diffrent screen size.

The flexBox is same as web but few exaptations as comparision the web.

1 The default direction is row in the web/ column

2 align-content default is stretch/flex-start

we normally use flex-direction, align-items,and justify-content for archive right layout.
